For your convenience, I can be directed to manage garrisons or production.  When asked to 'Manage Garrisons', I will use available training facilities to provide garrisons on systems where they are required.  If directed to 'Manage Production', I will order our construction yards to produce mines and refineries in order to maximize our production and maintenance capabilities. You can issue any of these on-going commands to me by closing this message, right-clicking on my image in the Command Center, and selecting the appropriate command from my pop-up menu.